title: 4 Rare 80s Albums [Part 67] Post-Punk, New Wave, Gothic
description:
Well this seems to be the end of TPB. While I am disappointed like many others, I wish the guys the best of luck. Life moves on and so should we. Let's make the best of these couple of weeks left! I hope you'll enjoy these records as much as I do.

Headleaders - What It Means To Me [1983]

Jesus Couldn't Drum - The Best of

The Del-Bizanteens - Lies To Live By [1982]

The Vyllies - Lilith [1985]
